177
00:14:42,552 --> 00:14:43,637
But he...

178
00:14:47,641 --> 00:14:48,725
YONGHAN: Jinman.

179
00:14:49,643 --> 00:14:52,437
We're mercenaries.
We're not soldiers anymore.

180
00:14:53,605 --> 00:14:55,607
When you carry out
those types of operations,

181
00:14:55,690 --> 00:14:57,692
