205
00:17:36,184 --> 00:17:38,061
Shut the fuck up, Seongjo.

206
00:17:38,144 --> 00:17:39,437
Your dick will fall off.

207
00:17:40,063 --> 00:17:41,690
(SPEAKS ENGLISH) You talk too much.

208
00:17:42,899 --> 00:17:44,734
