My hands are tied.

258
00:21:00,972 --> 00:21:04,184
Also, there are no civilians
who will get in the way

259
00:21:04,267 --> 00:21:06,144
around the area of operations.

260
00:21:06,811 --> 00:21:07,812
Yonghan!

261
00:21:08,438 --> 00:21:09,481
